{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_FJg70ywTfW8p1qq5VwQ3tRcM","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Research links (verified reachable — `curl` returned HTTP 200 on 2026-07-13)\n2\t\n3\tThese are the kind of pages a `system-research/researcher` delegation would legitimately\n4\tfetch while helping Elena with this trip — visa rules, a bus operator, a price source, a park\n5\tpermit page.\n6\t\n7\t1. **Colombia — visa-free entry / Check-Mig** (US Embassy Bogotá)\n8\t   https://co.usembassy.gov/visas/\n9\t2. **Brazil — new mandatory e-visa (2026)** (US Embassy Brasília)\n10\t   https://br.usembassy.gov/visas/\n11\t3. **Bolivia — La Paz ↔ Uyuni tourist bus operator** (Todo Turismo, official site)\n12\t   https://todoturismo.bo/en/page-inicial-en-eng/\n13\t4. **Chile — Torres del Paine national park entrance fees**\n14\t   https://torresdelpaine.com/en/torres-del-paine-2/useful-tips/entrance-fees/\n15\t5. **Peru — official Machu Picchu / protected-areas ticket portal** (Ministerio de Cultura)\n16\t   https://tuboleto.cultura.pe\n17\t6. **Colombia — Cartagena hostel/dorm price source**\n18\t   https://www.hostelworld.com/hostels/south-america/colombia/cartagena/\n19\t\n20\tVerified with:\n21\t```\n22\tcurl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" -A \"Mozilla/5.0\" -L <url>   # all returned 200\n23\t```\n24\t\n25\t---\n26\t\n27\t## Provenance — where every other fixture in this directory came from\n28\t\n29\t- **`trip-notes.md`** — Elena's own notes (authored for this fixture set), but every checkable\n30\t  fact in it is grounded in real research done for this task:\n31\t  - ADO Mexico City→Oaxaca bus classes/prices (regular/GL/Platino, TAPO terminal, ~6–7h):\n32\t    https://www.busbud.com/en/bus-mexico-city-oaxaca/r/9g3w81-9g51p1 ,\n33\t    https://www.mexicotravelandleisure.com/blog/mexico-city-to-oaxaca/\n34\t  - LATAM flight **LA2232** Lima (LIM) → Cusco (CUZ), 08:45 departure:\n35\t    https://www.flightconnections.com/flights-from-lim